  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA8">
<l>arukum cuvaṭun terivuṇarō maṉpē</l>
<l>peruku mikavituveṉ pēcīr parukalām</l>
<l>paṇpuṭaiyīr pāraḷantīr pāviyeṅkaṭ kāṇpariya</l>
<l>nuṇpuṭaiyīr nummai numakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We do not perceive with a clarity that gets near to [and] tastes you. Love</l>
<l>for you, it is great. What is this? Speak, you who possess the quality</l>
<l>that is drinking, you who measured the earth, you who have minuteness</l>
<l>difficult to see for the eyes of us sinners.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
